    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, pristine ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve definitely found it. I'm happy to answer any questions you have\u2014come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
