    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of automotive engineering, maintained to an exacting standard. This specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated V8 powerplant mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The longitudinal chassis remains perfectly balanced, benefiting from a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a rigid subframe free of any structural fatigue. Every bushing is tight, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances. Performance is anchored by ventilated, cross-drilled rotors providing exceptional thermal management. Cosmetically, the finish retains its deep factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. Inside, the ergonomic cockpit shows no bolster wear, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous mechanical sympathy.",
